{"tid":1449074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［立此存照］812 香港人 勿忘初衷","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:52:51.000Z","uid":176765,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"71a39d76aceeb95fa6bd1bf1c47141c836731326","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"求每一位香港人緊記你地812今晚見到既一切<br />\n<br />\n緊記過去發生過既每一樣違背良知既事<br />\n<br />\n緊記你地有幾撚嬲 有幾撚傷心 有幾撚心痛 <br />\n<br />\n抗爭 剩下成功 沒有失敗<br />\n<br />\n要記得不分化 不割蓆 不督灰既背後<br />\n<br />\n每個人都係為自己既良知 人性去抗爭<br />\n<br />\n我地被政權逼使至 剩下成功<br />\n<br />\n帶著依份永世不忘既感覺 <br />\n<br />\n去冷靜思考抗爭既去向<br />\n<br />\n要成功 要有勿忘初衷既心態 <br />\n<br />\n記著你依一刻既感覺 直到永遠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勿忘初衷</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a92fc2c5cd97e01e03583902f219a71fba033d3","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7c06c9e797f48ff78ca99e2910344d43d0afeea","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e44cf7bbb8ee43b8ce3287a1770dd17c0c180fb","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfecd270dd1359ce59939591e6e6b87ee4ace209","tid":1449074,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d44b63db47843636f21b9fb104c9b5b4a98af10","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5aaf78a782402c135e27c0ef2c482f6e4ec817f","tid":1449074,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是我們責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」"},{"pid":"f4cd5732f664af213334eb5b3015d93327fa90a1","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c571967042fe9ac9420379898145bba66359388","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:51:39.000Z","msg":"請保持抗爭心態<br />\n香港人並不善忘"},{"pid":"46d5cb59574615e14e5edadbaab942945eea6045","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"請保持抗爭心態<br />\n香港人並不善忘"},{"pid":"d9c442b2776f839ed7e508afc8bc8ae0fa75ca36","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"請保持抗爭心態<br />\n香港人並不善忘"},{"pid":"362e28b3b172c0945d35793465d460cae319ff4e","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:26.000Z","msg":"請保持抗爭心態<br />\n香港人並不善忘"},{"pid":"2e6bb4e5cf20cd7cf1b2e974014864c1cf0564af","tid":1449074,"uid":176765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"請保持抗爭心態<br />\n香港人並不善忘"},{"pid":"bfe7c0e0c30ff4428c3f344d6d29b0947a5f5634","tid":1449074,"uid":280271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"請保持抗爭心態<br />\n香港人並不善忘"},{